title: The U.S. Treasury, The TARP Recipients in the lower 48 states,USA, Feb 2009
name: The U.S. Treasury, The TARP Recipients in the lower 48 states,USA, Feb 2009
description:
The point shapefile shows the geocoded locations in the lower 48 states of those institutions who received TARP funds, an euphemism for the tax payer bailout! 
The list is based on a report titled "Capital Purchase Program" released by the U.S. Treasury Dept's Office of Financial Stability, dated Feb 20, 2009.
